pMaybe you#8217;re using a href=http://akismet.com/Akismet/a to stop spam in its tracks, a href=http://vaultpress.com/VaultPress/a to keep your site safe and secure, and a href=http://polldaddy.comPolldaddy/a to find out what your readers are thinking. Maybe you#8217;re using a href=http://wordpress.comWordPress.com/a to build a fancy new site, or a href=http://jetpack.meJetpack/a to supercharge your self-hosted one./p
pNow you can sign into all these awesome services, including Akismet, with just one account #8212; your WordPress.com account!/p
h2Signing into Akismet/h2
pStarting today, you#8217;ll be required to sign into Akismet with your WordPress.com account./p
pThe good news is, if you have an Akismet account, you already have a WordPress.com account! Simply a href=https://akismet.com/account/sign into Akismet/a with the credentials you#8217;ve been using all along./p
pstrongDon#8217;t have a free WordPress.com account?/strong/p
pThere#8217;s a good chance you already have one, and don#8217;t realize it! Try a href=https://akismet.com/account/signing into Akismet/a with the credentials you#8217;ve been using all along./p
pIf you really don#8217;t have a WordPress.com account, it only takes a few seconds to sign up and is totally free! Simply click #8220;Sign in with WordPress.com#8221; on the a href=https://akismet.com/account/Akismet account page/a, and then click the #8220;Need an account?#8221; link./p
pimg class=alignnone size-medium wp-image-942 alt=signin1 src=http://akismet.files.wordpress.com/2013/01/signin1.jpeg?w=600h=348 width=600 height=348 //p
pstrongAlready have a WordPress.com account?/strong/p
pstrong/strongYou#8217;re all set! Go ahead and a href=http://akismet.com/account/sign into Akismet/a with your fancy WordPress.com account. You might be asked to #8220;authorize#8221; Akismet to access your WordPress.com account./p
pimg class=alignnone size-medium wp-image-943 alt=signin2 src=http://akismet.files.wordpress.com/2013/01/signin2.jpeg?w=600h=231 width=600 height=231 //p
pstrongNot sure if you have a WordPress.com account?/strong/p
pNo problem! If you use VaultPress, Polldaddy, Jetpack, IntenseDebate, or Gravatar, you can just sign in with the same account you use for them. Otherwise, just go ahead and try a href=https://akismet.com/account/signing into Akismet/a with the credentials you#8217;ve been using to sign into Akismet all along./p
pIf it turns out that you don#8217;t have a WordPress.com account, you can sign up for a free account in a flash! Simply click #8220;Sign in with WordPress.com#8221; on the a href=https://akismet.com/account/Akismet account page/a, and then click the #8220;Need an account?#8221; link. We#8217;ll let you know if we find one that#8217;s tied to your email address./p
pstrongHave any questions?/strong/p
